
## **5. docs/features.md**

```markdown
# Detailed Features Documentation

## Authentication & Security

### User Management
- **Multi-role System**: Investigator, Admin, Viewer roles
- **Password Policies**: Minimum 8 characters, mixed case, numbers, special characters
- **Account Lockout**: Automatic lockout after 5 failed attempts
- **Session Management**: 24-hour session timeout

### Security Features
- **AES-256 Encryption**: All data encrypted at rest
- **SHA-256 Hashing**: Password hashing with salt
- **Input Sanitization**: Protection against XSS attacks
- **Audit Logging**: Complete trail of all user actions

## Case Management

### Creating Cases
- **Case Number Generation**: Automatic unique case numbers
- **Priority Levels**: Low, Medium, High, Critical
- **Tag System**: Categorize cases with custom tags
- **Description Fields**: Detailed case documentation

### Case Organization
- **Search & Filter**: Find cases by number, title, or tags
- **Sorting Options**: Sort by date, priority, or status
- **Bulk Operations**: Import multiple files at once
- **Evidence Linking**: Connect evidence to specific cases

## Evidence Management

### File Upload
- **Multiple Formats**: Images, documents, archives, logs
- **Size Limits**: Configurable file size limits (default: 100MB)
- **Type Validation**: Whitelist of allowed file types
- **Batch Upload**: Upload multiple files simultaneously

### Evidence Processing
- **Automatic Metadata Extraction**: Extract file information
- **Hash Generation**: Calculate MD5, SHA-1, SHA-256 hashes
- **EXIF Data**: Extract camera and location data from images
- **File Integrity**: Verify file integrity through hashing

## Forensic Analysis

### Metadata Analysis
- **File Information**: Size, type, timestamps, attributes
- **EXIF Data**: Camera make/model, GPS coordinates, timestamps
- **System Information**: File paths, permissions, ownership
- **Technical Data**: Dimensions, format, compression

### Analysis Tools
- **Hex Viewer**: Binary file examination
- **String Search**: Search for patterns in files
- **Hash Verification**: Verify file integrity
- **Timeline Analysis**: Chronological event reconstruction

### Artifact Analysis
- **Browser History**: Extract browsing history
- **USB Device Logs**: Track USB device connections
- **System Logs**: Analyze system events
- **Recent Files**: Track file access patterns

## Reporting System

### Report Generation
- **Multiple Formats**: PDF, HTML, CSV exports
- **Custom Templates**: Create custom report templates
- **Automated Generation**: Schedule automatic reports
- **Data Visualization**: Charts and graphs for analysis

### Report Content
- **Case Summary**: Overview of case details
- **Evidence List**: Complete evidence inventory
- **Analysis Results**: Findings and observations
- **Recommendations**: Suggested next steps
- **Chain of Custody**: Evidence handling documentation

## User Interface

### Dashboard
- **Statistics**: Case counts, evidence items, pending analysis
- **Recent Activity**: Latest user actions
- **Quick Actions**: Common tasks shortcuts
- **Notifications**: System alerts and updates

### Navigation
- **Sidebar Menu**: Organized by function
- **Breadcrumbs**: Track navigation path
- **Search**: Global search across all data
- **Filters**: Advanced filtering options

### Responsive Design
- **Desktop Optimization**: Full feature set on large screens
- **Tablet Support**: Adapted interface for tablets
- **Mobile Responsive**: Basic functionality on mobile devices

## Data Management

### Storage
- **LocalStorage**: Client-side data storage
- **Encryption**: All sensitive data encrypted
- **Backup**: Manual backup and restore
- **Export**: Data export in JSON format

### Data Integrity
- **Hash Verification**: Verify data integrity
- **Audit Trail**: Track all data modifications
- **Version Control**: Track changes to cases
- **Validation**: Data validation on input

## Integration Capabilities

### File System Integration
- **Local File Access**: Import from local file system
- **Drag & Drop**: Easy file upload interface
- **Folder Import**: Import entire folders
- **External Storage**: Support for external drives

### Browser Integration
- **Bookmarklets**: Quick capture tools
- **Browser Extensions**: Evidence collection tools
- **API Access**: REST API for integration
- **Webhooks**: Notification system

## Administration

### User Administration
- **User Management**: Create, edit, delete users
- **Role Assignment**: Assign permissions by role
- **Activity Monitoring**: Monitor user activities
- **Access Control**: Granular permission system

### System Configuration
- **Settings Management**: Configure application settings
- **Security Configuration**: Adjust security parameters
- **Backup Configuration**: Schedule automatic backups
- **Log Management**: View and manage system logs

## Advanced Features

### Timeline Analysis
- **Event Correlation**: Connect related events
- **Visual Timeline**: Graphical event representation
- **Time Filtering**: Filter events by time range
- **Event Types**: Categorize events by type

### Hash Analysis
- **Hash Databases**: Compare against known hash databases
- **Hash Collision Detection**: Identify potential collisions
- **Batch Hashing**: Hash multiple files simultaneously
- **Hash Verification**: Verify evidence integrity

### Memory Analysis
- **Process Analysis**: Analyze running processes
- **Network Connections**: Examine network activity
- **Memory Dumps**: Analyze memory dump files
- **Artifact Extraction**: Extract artifacts from memory

## Performance & Optimization

### Performance Features
- **Lazy Loading**: Load data as needed
- **Caching**: Cache frequently accessed data
- **Compression**: Compress data for storage
- **Optimization**: Performance optimizations

### Scalability
- **Large Datasets**: Handle large evidence collections
- **Multiple Users**: Support concurrent users
- **High Performance**: Optimized for speed
- **Resource Management**: Efficient resource usage

## Security & Compliance

### Compliance Features
- **Audit Trail**: Complete activity logging
- **Data Retention**: Configurable data retention
- **Privacy Controls**: User privacy protections
- **Compliance Reports**: Generate compliance reports

### Security Controls
- **Access Logging**: Log all access attempts
- **Data Encryption**: End-to-end encryption
- **Security Audits**: Regular security audits
- **Vulnerability Scanning**: Security vulnerability checks
